featureboard.Text_1: Kia rangona to reo! E whakaae ana koe me whakawhanake tatou i tetahi ahuatanga, bug ranei? Patohia te paatene hei tautoko.
featureboard.Text_2: Kei te hiahia maatau ki te whakawhanake i tetahi waahanga hou? Whakaahuatia i raro nei.
featureboard.Text_3: Ia wiki ka tiimata taatau ki te whakawhanake i te waahanga nui e tonohia ana e te hapori. Ko nga moni katoa i koha mai ka haere ki tera kaupapa, ka taea e taatau te whakapai ake i te taupānga.
featureboard.Text_4: Ko nga moni katoa i kohaina ka whakamahia hei utu i a maatau utu whanaketanga.
featureboard.Text_5: He whakaaro koe mo tetahi ahuatanga, whakatika bug ranei e hiahia ana koe kia mahia e matou engari kaore ano kia kite i etahi atu taapiri? Whakaahuatia i raro nei:

Options.text: $400 Huinga ataata i te wa tuturu
$200 Nga korero rehitatanga tuatahi o te rohe
$130 Tirotiro me te tiri i nga mano o {{1}} meme

featureboard.RequestNewFeature: Tonoa he waahanga hou / whakatika bug

contribute.ContributeExplanation: Awhina ki te tautoko i te whanaketanga tonu o te {{communityName}} taupānga. Ko o takoha katoa ka awhina ki te whakatika i nga pepeke me te whakawhanake i nga ahuatanga hou hei awhina i te whakatipu i te hapori ipurangi!
contribute.ReasonToContribute: Ko tenei taupānga ka tiakina e nga kaitautoko o {{communityName}}. Awhina ki te tautoko i tenei taupānga kia whai hua ai tatou ki te oranga o te tangata!
